Abuse is what you folks need to avoid.  Not saying anyone to this point wants to abuse it, but there are a lot of underhanded people out there.  And if someone EVER sold a spot on this list that would be a sad and sick thing, both for the seller and the buyer.<br>
<br>
Well, I am done.  Sorry to be a backseat driver.  My opinions should be moved the the &quot;disregard&quot; stack now that I am not in charge. <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->  <p>Fayenae <BR>
